text: Gurpreet Singh was born 29 October 1979 is representative for India in the sport of Kabaddi. He was a member of the kabaddi team that won a gold medal in the 2014 Asian Games in Incheon. ==References== Category:Living people Category:1979 births Category:Indian kabaddi players Category:Asian Games medalists in kabaddi Category:Kabaddi players at the 2014 Asian Games Category:Asian Games gold medalists for India Category:Medalists at the 2014 Asian Games Category:Pro Kabaddi League players
title: Gurpreet Singh (kabaddi)
